description:
deer is an application based on the MOOSE framework (https://mooseframework.org/) developed at Idaho National
Laboratory. The application extends the framework to handle structural problems with a consistent large deformation
framework as well as adding miscellaneous utility routines we have found useful in our work on high temperature
structural design.
